{"tid":562933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支蟈春晚節目惹上非議  涉嫌種族歧視黑人","createTime":"2018-02-16T11:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T11:32:13.000Z","uid":1239,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"17fda0fff5a416ac035caecc05360d8c3294e640","tid":562933,"uid":1239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/16/192523_744edf9fdf25b321ca40a8c995e88f63.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F16%2F192523_744edf9fdf25b321ca40a8c995e88f63.png&h=ecd27885&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/16/192526_5f5364d1b71c21b6e4fdd1b2bd5e5d1d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F16%2F192526_5f5364d1b71c21b6e4fdd1b2bd5e5d1d.png&h=a2bd0d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA skit on China's biggest Lunar New Year TV show has sparked widespread criticism and accusations of racism.<br />\n<br />\nIn a comedy routine celebrating Chinese-African ties an Asian actress appears in blackface and with exaggerated buttocks.<br />\n<br />\nUsing make-up to lampoon black people - a practice known as blackface - is seen by many as deeply offensive.<br />\n<br />\nThe annual state media variety show is hugely popular, and has up to 800 million viewers.<br />\n<br />\nSome observers have pointed out that this sketch would not have been intended as offensive to Africans.<br />\n<br />\nHowever, this is not the first time Chinese entertainment shows have caused controversy with their portrayals of other ethnicities.<br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/amp/world-asia-china-43081218#click=https://t.co/IrOQefNqPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Famp%2Fworld-asia-china-43081218%23click%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FIrOQefNqPI&d=y8Uj6sQNro%2FuKFV%2B%2B0MCuAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=7458abc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/amp/world-asia-china-43081218#click=https://t.co/IrOQefNqPI</a>"},{"pid":"04c8393e61a53967eb2bf2408becf9489c6a82e3","tid":562933,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:28:21.000Z","msg":"不意外"},{"pid":"2ec878833701de50b921cda7f57056266e0dc2d0","tid":562933,"uid":49197,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:30:22.000Z","msg":"我平生最憎兩種人，一種係種族歧視既人，一種係nigger"},{"pid":"35cc5eaaac885c58502673ba0ff1e2e23bc99d42","tid":562933,"uid":135445,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ec878833701de50b921cda7f57056266e0dc2d0","tid":562933,"uid":49197,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:30:22.000Z","msg":"我平生最憎兩種人，一種係種族歧視既人，一種係nigger"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:31:19.000Z","msg":"你憎唔憎自己?"},{"pid":"7a216c6b2b7e3b83f6cd4b07420a3d1ac3b45963","tid":562933,"uid":137248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:32:13.000Z","msg":"連登仔就不嬲都歧視開黑人<br />\n但又討厭支那<br />\n不次會撐邊面??"}]}